data.description: This stunning white brick home with black trim is a true gem. Built in 2022, and offers modern features and a great location close to the interstate. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by a bright and open floor plan. The living room boasts a cozy fireplace and beautiful wood beams, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere. The neutral color palette throughout the house provides a blank canvas for you to make it your own. The kitchen is a chef's dream, featuring custom cabinets, stainless steel appliances, and a large pantry. Beautiful finishes in both the kitchen and bathrooms add an elegant touch to the space. In the primary bathroom, you'll find dual sinks, a custom tiled walk-in shower, luxurious soaker tub, and under vanity lighting that creates a desirable ambiance. The split bedroom floor plan offers privacy and convenience. The primary bedroom has easy access to an ensuite bathroom and a large closet that leads directly into the laundry room. Outside, you'll find a low maintenance yard and a covered back patio where you can relax and enjoy your morning coffee, and a 2-car garage with extra parking for guests. Call today and schedule your private showing.
